View

Class UserAlbumViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • View.UserAlbumViewController

  • public class UserAlbumViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    UserAlbumViewController is the class associated with the User homepage for all albums. In this page the user can search for photos by tags or dates and see all existing albums. The albums show the date ranges, earliest photo, number of photos in album, and the name of the album. The User can make a new album, open an existing album, and delete an album on this page
    Author:
    Tom Raybould & Mike Tomkowich
